  <h1 id="maincontent">BECAUSE THESE KIDS ARE</h1>
  <p>Producers: Elizabeta Vidovic, Kathryn Michelle and Izabela Vidovic</p>
    <p>A 10-minute dramatic film from the heart of 12-year-old actress, Izabela Vidovic. While at a park, a young artist sees a bullying situation unfold in front of her and those involved become the muses for her work. When the person bullying suddenly targets her, she surrenders her pictures to him, opening his eyes to the truth behind who he and these kids really are.</p>
	
